# üêû bug report

### Affected Package
@angular/core

### Is this a regression?

Not sure. The bug appears in both Angular 7 and 8.

### Description

The `ngAfterViewInit` lifecycle hook isn't called for a component that is transcluded using `<ng-content>` which itself is within an `*ngIf`.


## üî¨ Minimal Reproduction

https://stackblitz.com/edit/angular-playground-vqhjuh

## üî• Exception or Error

No error, but the hooks aren't called at the correct time.

